{
  "name": "quest",
  "displayName": "Quest - Query Studio",
  "description": "Quest - Query Azure Data Explorer (Kusto), Azure DevOps (WIQL), and Outlook with AI assistance",
  "version": "0.5.7",
  "publisher": "inbar-rotem",
  "license": "MIT",
  "icon": "resources/icon.png",
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/InbarR/Quest.git"
  },
  "homepage": "https://github.com/InbarR/Quest#readme",
  "bugs": {
    "url": "https://github.com/InbarR/Quest/issues"
  },
  "engines": {
    "vscode": "^1.85.0"
  },
  "categories": [
    "Data Science",
    "Programming Languages",
    "Other"
  ],
  "keywords": [
    "kusto",
    "kql",
    "azure data explorer",
    "azure devops",
    "wiql",
    "outlook",
    "oql",
    "query",
    "ai",
    "copilot"
  ],
  "activationEvents": [
    "onLanguage:kql",
    "onLanguage:wiql",
    "onLanguage:oql",
    "onView:querystudio.clusters",
    "onCommand:queryStudio.newKqlFile",
    "onCommand:queryStudio.newWiqlFile",
    "onCommand:queryStudio.newOqlFile",
    "onUri"
  ],
  "main": "./out/extension.js",
  "contributes": {
    "viewsContainers": {
      "activitybar": [
        {
          "id": "queryStudio",
          "title": "Quest",
          "icon": "resources/quest.svg"
        },
        {
          "id": "queryStudioAI",
          "title": "Quest AI",
          "icon": "$(hubot)"
        }
      ],
      "panel": [
        {
          "id": "queryStudioResults",
          "title": "Query Results",
          "icon": "$(table)"
        }
      ]
    },
    "views": {
      "queryStudio": [
        {
          "id": "querystudio.clusters",
          "name": "Data Sources",
          "icon": "$(database)"
        },
        {
          "id": "querystudio.presets",
          "name": "‚≠ê Favorites",
          "type": "webview"
        },
        {
          "id": "querystudio.history",
          "name": "üìú History",
          "type": "webview"
        },
        {
          "id": "querystudio.resultsHistory",
          "name": "Saved Results",
          "type": "webview"
        },
        {
          "id": "querystudio.snippets",
          "name": "üìù Snippets",
          "type": "webview"
        }
      ],
      "queryStudioAI": [
        {
          "id": "querystudio.aiChat",
          "name": "ü§ñ Quest Chat",
          "type": "webview"
        }
      ],
      "queryStudioResults": [
        {
          "id": "querystudio.results",
          "name": "Results",
          "type": "webview"
        }
      ]
    },
    "viewsWelcome": [
      {
        "view": "querystudio.clusters",
        "contents": "No data sources configured.\n\n[$(add) Add Data Source](command:queryStudio.addDataSource)",
        "when": "!queryStudio.isOutlookMode"
      },
      {
        "view": "querystudio.clusters",
        "contents": "Outlook mode uses your local Outlook installation.\n\nNo configuration needed - just run your OQL queries!",
        "when": "queryStudio.isOutlookMode"
      }
    ],
    "languages": [
      {
        "id": "kql",
        "aliases": [
          "KQL",
          "Kusto Query Language",
          "kusto"
        ],
        "extensions": [
          ".kql",
          ".kusto",
          ".csl"
        ],
        "configuration": "./language-configuration.json"
      },
      {
        "id": "wiql",
        "aliases": [
          "WIQL",
          "Work Item Query Language"
        ],
        "extensions": [
          ".wiql"
        ],
        "configuration": "./language-configuration.json"
      },
      {
        "id": "oql",
        "aliases": [
          "OQL",
          "Outlook Query Language",
          "outlook"
        ],
        "extensions": [
          ".oql"
        ],
        "configuration": "./language-configuration.json"
      }
    ],
    "grammars": [
      {
        "language": "kql",
        "scopeName": "source.kql",
        "path": "./syntaxes/kql.tmLanguage.json"
      },
      {
        "language": "wiql",
        "scopeName": "source.wiql",
        "path": "./syntaxes/wiql.tmLanguage.json"
      },
      {
        "language": "oql",
        "scopeName": "source.oql",
        "path": "./syntaxes/oql.tmLanguage.json"
      }
    ],
    "commands": [
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.welcome",
        "title": "Welcome / Getting Started",
        "icon": "$(question)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.showPanel",
        "title": "Quest",
        "shortTitle": "Quest",
        "icon": "$(database)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.runQuery",
        "title": "Run Query",
        "shortTitle": "Run",
        "icon": "$(rocket)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.runQueryAlternate",
        "title": "Run Query in Same Tab",
        "shortTitle": "Run ‚Ü∫",
        "icon": "$(sync)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.cancelQuery",
        "title": "Cancel Query",
        "icon": "$(stop-circle)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.newKqlFile",
        "title": "New KQL Query",
        "icon": "$(new-file)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.newWiqlFile",
        "title": "New WIQL Query",
        "icon": "$(new-file)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.newOqlFile",
        "title": "New Outlook Query",
        "icon": "$(new-file)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.newQuery",
        "title": "New Query",
        "icon": "$(new-file)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.saveAsPreset",
        "title": "Save as Favorite",
        "icon": "$(star-add)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.addDataSource",
        "title": "Add Data Source",
        "icon": "$(add)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.showExample",
        "title": "Show Example Query",
        "icon": "$(lightbulb)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.setResultsLimit",
        "title": "Set Results Limit",
        "icon": "$(list-ordered)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.refreshClusters",
        "title": "Refresh Data Sources",
        "icon": "$(refresh)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.setActiveCluster",
        "title": "Set as Active",
        "icon": "$(check)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.removeCluster",
        "title": "Remove",
        "icon": "$(trash)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.renameCluster",
        "title": "Rename",
        "icon": "$(edit)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.toggleFavorite",
        "title": "Toggle Favorite",
        "icon": "$(star)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.loadPreset",
        "title": "Load Query",
        "icon": "$(go-to-file)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.deletePreset",
        "title": "Delete Favorite",
        "icon": "$(trash)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.aiChat",
        "title": "Open AI Chat",
        "icon": "$(hubot)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.aiExplain",
        "title": "Explain Query with AI",
        "icon": "$(lightbulb)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.aiGenerate",
        "title": "Generate Query with AI",
        "icon": "$(sparkle)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.resetAiToken",
        "title": "Reset AI Authentication Token",
        "icon": "$(key)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.manageAiPersonas",
        "title": "Manage AI Personas",
        "icon": "$(account)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.selectAiPersona",
        "title": "Select AI Persona",
        "icon": "$(account)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.reportIssue",
        "title": "Send Feedback",
        "icon": "$(feedback)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.exportResults",
        "title": "Export Results",
        "icon": "$(export)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.refreshFavorites",
        "title": "Refresh Favorites",
        "icon": "$(refresh)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.refreshHistory",
        "title": "Refresh History",
        "icon": "$(refresh)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.clearHistory",
        "title": "Clear History",
        "icon": "$(trash)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.copyClusterInfo",
        "title": "Copy Connection Info",
        "icon": "$(copy)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.exportAllClusters",
        "title": "Export All Data Sources",
        "icon": "$(export)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.toggleMode",
        "title": "Toggle Kusto/ADO Mode",
        "icon": "$(arrow-swap)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.setMode",
        "title": "Set Query Mode",
        "icon": "$(settings)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.fetchSchema",
        "title": "Fetch Schema",
        "icon": "$(cloud-download)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.refreshSchema",
        "title": "Refresh Schema for Active Database",
        "icon": "$(sync)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.clearSchemaCache",
        "title": "Clear Schema Cache",
        "icon": "$(trash)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.refreshResultsHistory",
        "title": "Refresh Results History",
        "icon": "$(refresh)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.showKeyboardShortcuts",
        "title": "Show Keyboard Shortcuts",
        "icon": "$(keyboard)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.insertSnippet",
        "title": "Insert Snippet",
        "icon": "$(insert)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.saveSnippet",
        "title": "Save Selection as Snippet",
        "icon": "$(add)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.refreshSnippets",
        "title": "Refresh Snippets",
        "icon": "$(refresh)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.saveConnectionProfile",
        "title": "Save Current Connection as Profile",
        "icon": "$(save)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.switchConnectionProfile",
        "title": "Switch Connection Profile",
        "icon": "$(plug)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.deleteConnectionProfile",
        "title": "Delete Connection Profile",
        "icon": "$(trash)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.pasteAsTable",
        "title": "Paste Data as Table",
        "icon": "$(clippy)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.openTableFromFile",
        "title": "Open File as Table",
        "icon": "$(table)",
        "category": "Quest"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.viewExternalData",
        "title": "View Data as Table",
        "icon": "$(table)",
        "category": "Quest"
      }
    ],
    "keybindings": [
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.runQuery",
        "key": "F5",
        "when": "editorTextFocus && (editorLangId == kql || editorLangId == wiql || editorLangId == oql)"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.runQueryAlternate",
        "key": "ctrl+shift+enter",
        "when": "editorTextFocus && (editorLangId == kql || editorLangId == wiql || editorLangId == oql)"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.cancelQuery",
        "key": "shift+F5",
        "when": "editorTextFocus && (editorLangId == kql || editorLangId == wiql || editorLangId == oql)"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.saveAsPreset",
        "key": "ctrl+shift+s",
        "when": "editorTextFocus && (editorLangId == kql || editorLangId == wiql || editorLangId == oql)"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.aiChat",
        "key": "ctrl+shift+a",
        "when": "editorTextFocus && (editorLangId == kql || editorLangId == wiql || editorLangId == oql)"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.reportIssue",
        "key": "ctrl+shift+b"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.showKeyboardShortcuts",
        "key": "ctrl+shift+/",
        "when": "editorTextFocus && (editorLangId == kql || editorLangId == wiql || editorLangId == oql)"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.toggleMode",
        "key": "ctrl+alt+m",
        "when": "editorTextFocus && (editorLangId == kql || editorLangId == wiql || editorLangId == oql)"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.switchConnectionProfile",
        "key": "ctrl+alt+p",
        "when": "editorTextFocus && (editorLangId == kql || editorLangId == wiql || editorLangId == oql)"
      },
      {
        "command": "queryStudio.pasteAsTable",
        "key": "ctrl+alt+v",
        "mac": "cmd+alt+v"
      }
    ],
    "submenus": [
      {
        "id": "queryStudio.runSubmenu",
        "label": "Run Query",
        "icon": "$(run)"
      },
      {
        "id": "queryStudio.contextSubmenu",
        "label": "Quest"
      }
    ],
    "menus": {
      "queryStudio.runSubmenu": [
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.runQuery",
          "group": "1_run@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.runQueryAlternate",
          "group": "1_run@2"
        }
      ],
      "editor/title": [
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.showPanel",
          "when": "editorLangId == kql || editorLangId == wiql || editorLangId == oql",
          "group": "navigation@0"
        },
        {
          "submenu": "queryStudio.runSubmenu",
          "when": "editorLangId == kql || editorLangId == wiql || editorLangId == oql",
          "group": "navigation@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.showExample",
          "when": "editorLangId == kql || editorLangId == wiql || editorLangId == oql",
          "group": "navigation@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.aiChat",
          "when": "editorLangId == kql || editorLangId == wiql || editorLangId == oql",
          "group": "navigation@3"
        }
      ],
      "queryStudio.contextSubmenu": [
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.runQuery",
          "group": "1_run@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.aiChat",
          "group": "2_ai@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.aiExplain",
          "group": "2_ai@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.saveAsPreset",
          "group": "3_save@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.showExample",
          "group": "4_help@1"
        }
      ],
      "editor/context": [
        {
          "submenu": "queryStudio.contextSubmenu",
          "when": "editorLangId == kql || editorLangId == wiql || editorLangId == oql",
          "group": "queryStudio"
        }
      ],
      "view/title": [
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.newQuery",
          "when": "view == querystudio.clusters",
          "group": "navigation@0"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.toggleMode",
          "when": "view == querystudio.clusters",
          "group": "navigation@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.refreshClusters",
          "when": "view == querystudio.clusters",
          "group": "navigation@4"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.fetchSchema",
          "when": "view == querystudio.clusters",
          "group": "navigation@3"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.addDataSource",
          "when": "view == querystudio.clusters && !queryStudio.isOutlookMode",
          "group": "navigation@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.exportAllClusters",
          "when": "view == querystudio.clusters",
          "group": "2_export"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.refreshFavorites",
          "when": "view == querystudio.presets",
          "group": "navigation"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.refreshHistory",
          "when": "view == querystudio.history",
          "group": "navigation@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.clearHistory",
          "when": "view == querystudio.history",
          "group": "navigation@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.refreshResultsHistory",
          "when": "view == querystudio.resultsHistory",
          "group": "navigation"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.pasteAsTable",
          "when": "view == querystudio.results",
          "group": "navigation@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.openTableFromFile",
          "when": "view == querystudio.results",
          "group": "navigation@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.refreshSnippets",
          "when": "view == querystudio.snippets",
          "group": "navigation"
        }
      ],
      "view/item/context": [
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.toggleFavorite",
          "when": "view == querystudio.clusters && viewItem == cluster",
          "group": "1_actions"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.copyClusterInfo",
          "when": "view == querystudio.clusters && viewItem == cluster",
          "group": "1_actions"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.renameCluster",
          "when": "view == querystudio.clusters && viewItem == cluster",
          "group": "2_modify@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.removeCluster",
          "when": "view == querystudio.clusters && viewItem == cluster",
          "group": "2_modify@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.fetchSchema",
          "when": "view == querystudio.clusters && viewItem == database",
          "group": "1_actions"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.renameCluster",
          "when": "view == querystudio.clusters && viewItem == database",
          "group": "2_modify@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.removeCluster",
          "when": "view == querystudio.clusters && viewItem == database",
          "group": "2_modify@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.loadPreset",
          "when": "view == querystudio.presets && viewItem == preset",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "queryStudio.deletePreset",
          "when": "view == querystudio.presets && viewItem == preset",
          "group": "2_modify"
        }
      ]
    },
    "configuration": {
      "title": "Quest",
      "properties": {
        "queryStudio.defaultCluster": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "description": "Default Kusto cluster URL"
        },
        "queryStudio.defaultDatabase": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "description": "Default database name"
        },
        "queryStudio.ado.defaultAreaPath": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "description": "Default Area Path for Azure DevOps queries (e.g., 'MyProject\\MyTeam')"
        },
        "queryStudio.ado.defaultProject": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "description": "Default Azure DevOps project name"
        },
        "queryStudio.queryTimeout": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 300,
          "description": "Query timeout in seconds"
        },
        "queryStudio.maxResults": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 10000,
          "description": "Maximum number of rows to return"
        },
        "queryStudio.results.openInNewTab": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "description": "Open query results in a new tab (true) or replace the current results tab (false)"
        },
        "queryStudio.autoSaveHistory": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "description": "Automatically save executed queries to history"
        },
        "queryStudio.feedbackFormId": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "description": "Formspree form ID for feedback submissions (get one at formspree.io)"
        },
        "queryStudio.ai.enabled": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "description": "Enable AI features"
        },
        "queryStudio.ai.provider": {
          "type": "string",
          "enum": [
            "github",
            "azure",
            "copilot"
          ],
          "default": "github",
          "description": "AI provider to use"
        },
        "queryStudio.ai.model": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "gpt-4o-mini",
          "description": "AI model to use"
        },
        "queryStudio.ai.personas": {
          "type": "array",
          "default": [],
          "description": "Custom AI personas with different system prompts",
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "name": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "Display name for this persona"
              },
              "icon": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "Emoji or short text icon (e.g., 'ü§ñ' or 'E')"
              },
              "prompt": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "Custom instructions for this persona"
              }
            },
            "required": ["name", "prompt"]
          }
        },
        "queryStudio.ai.defaultPersona": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "description": "Name of the default persona to use (empty for default assistant)"
        },
        "queryStudio.sidecar.path": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "description": "Path to sidecar executable (leave empty for bundled)"
        },
        "queryStudio.history.retentionDays": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 30,
          "minimum": 1,
          "maximum": 365,
          "description": "Number of days to keep query history"
        },
        "queryStudio.history.maxItems": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 100,
          "minimum": 10,
          "maximum": 1000,
          "description": "Maximum number of history items to keep"
        },
        "queryStudio.resultsHistory.retentionDays": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 14,
          "minimum": 1,
          "maximum": 60,
          "description": "Number of days to keep results history"
        },
        "queryStudio.resultsHistory.maxItems": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 50,
          "minimum": 10,
          "maximum": 200,
          "description": "Maximum number of result items to keep"
        },
        "queryStudio.resultsHistory.maxSampleRows": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 10,
          "minimum": 0,
          "maximum": 100,
          "description": "Number of sample rows to store for each result (for preview)"
        }
      }
    },
    "walkthroughs": [
      {
        "id": "queryStudio.welcome",
        "title": "Get Started with Quest",
        "description": "Learn how to query Azure Data Explorer, Azure DevOps, and Outlook with AI assistance.",
        "steps": [
          {
            "id": "welcome",
            "title": "Welcome to Quest",
            "description": "Quest lets you query multiple data sources using familiar KQL-like syntax.\n\n**Supported data sources:**\n- **Kusto (KQL)** - Azure Data Explorer\n- **ADO (WIQL)** - Azure DevOps Work Items\n- **Outlook (OQL)** - Emails, Calendar, Contacts\n\n[Open Quest](command:workbench.view.extension.queryStudio)",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "resources/walkthrough/welcome.md"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "chooseMode",
            "title": "Choose Your Query Mode",
            "description": "Switch between query modes using the mode selector in the status bar or sidebar.\n\n**KQL Mode** - Query Azure Data Explorer clusters\n**ADO Mode** - Query Azure DevOps work items\n**Outlook Mode** - Query your local Outlook data\n\n[Toggle Mode](command:queryStudio.toggleMode)",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "resources/walkthrough/choose-mode.md"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "addDataSource",
            "title": "Add a Data Source",
            "description": "For Kusto and ADO modes, add your data sources to get started.\n\n**Kusto:** Add your cluster URL (e.g., `https://help.kusto.windows.net`)\n**ADO:** Add your organization URL (e.g., `https://dev.azure.com/myorg`)\n**Outlook:** No setup needed - uses your local Outlook!\n\n[Add Data Source](command:queryStudio.addDataSource)",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "resources/walkthrough/add-datasource.md"
            },
            "when": "!queryStudio.isOutlookMode"
          },
          {
            "id": "createQuery",
            "title": "Create Your First Query",
            "description": "Create a new query file and start writing queries.\n\n**KQL Example:**\n```\nStormEvents\n| where State == \"FLORIDA\"\n| take 10\n```\n\n**OQL Example:**\n```\nInbox\n| where Subject contains \"meeting\"\n| take 50\n```\n\n[New KQL Query](command:queryStudio.newKqlFile)\n[New Outlook Query](command:queryStudio.newOqlFile)",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "resources/walkthrough/create-query.md"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "runQuery",
            "title": "Run Your Query",
            "description": "Execute your query and see results instantly.\n\n**Keyboard shortcuts:**\n- **F5** - Run query\n- **Shift+F5** - Cancel query\n\nResults appear in the bottom panel with full export options.\n\n[Run Query](command:queryStudio.runQuery)",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "resources/walkthrough/run-query.md"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "aiAssistant",
            "title": "Use AI Assistant",
            "description": "Get AI-powered help with your queries!\n\n**Quick actions:**\n- **Fix** - Fix syntax errors\n- **Improve** - Optimize your query\n- **Explain** - Understand what a query does\n\nThe AI understands your favorites and recent queries for context-aware suggestions.\n\n[Open AI Chat](command:queryStudio.aiChat)",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "resources/walkthrough/ai-assistant.md"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "saveFavorites",
            "title": "Save Favorites & Snippets",
            "description": "Save your best queries for quick access.\n\n**Favorites** - Save complete queries with names\n**Snippets** - Save reusable query fragments\n**History** - Your recent queries are auto-saved\n\nUse **Ctrl+Shift+S** to save the current query.\n\n[Save as Favorite](command:queryStudio.saveAsPreset)",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "resources/walkthrough/favorites.md"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "shortcuts",
            "title": "Keyboard Shortcuts",
            "description": "Master Quest with these shortcuts:\n\n| Shortcut | Action |\n|----------|--------|\n| **F5** | Run Query |\n| **Shift+F5** | Cancel Query |\n| **Ctrl+Shift+S** | Save as Favorite |\n| **Ctrl+Shift+A** | Open AI Chat |\n| **Ctrl+Alt+M** | Toggle Mode |\n| **Ctrl+Shift+/** | Show All Shortcuts |\n\n[Show All Shortcuts](command:queryStudio.showKeyboardShortcuts)",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "resources/walkthrough/shortcuts.md"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
